WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:03.773
Sync and corrections by awaqeded
- www.addic7ed.com -

00:10.368 --> 00:13.537
Oh, come on.

00:13.538 --> 00:15.013
Not your day there, Cleary.

00:15.014 --> 00:17.908
All right, all right, all right.

00:17.909 --> 00:20.911
Here's the deal... I get a bull's-eye

00:20.912 --> 00:24.631
and Quinn buys a round.

00:24.632 --> 00:25.865
The day you get a bull's-eye, Cleary,

00:25.866 --> 00:27.366
is the day I suck off a horse.

00:29.786 --> 00:33.038
All right, fuck the pint.

00:33.039 --> 00:34.956
You're on.

00:38.378 --> 00:41.797
Yeah!

00:41.798 --> 00:44.299
Somebody find us a horny stallion!

00:44.300 --> 00:46.635
Open up, Quinn. Come on, open up.

00:46.636 --> 00:49.771
Come here. Hey, you forgot your hat.

00:54.727 --> 00:57.112
- He thought I was serious.
- Weren't you?

00:57.113 --> 01:00.315
I'd have let him go before
the horse drizzled him good.

